trans-unit.source: Represents a 3-D rectangle: for example, a cube.
trans-unit.target: 3 차원 사각형을 나타내는: 큐브 예를 들어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Rect3D is defined as a location (<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point3D>) and a size structure (<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Size3D>).
trans-unit.target: Rect3D 위치로 정의 됩니다 (<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point3D>) 및 크기의 구조체 (<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Size3D>).</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Size3D> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point3D>

trans-unit.source: Because the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.X%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Y%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Z%2A> values specified for the size are magnitudes and not coordinates, they cannot be negative except in the case of an empty rectangle.
trans-unit.target: 때문에 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.X%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Y%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Z%2A>크기에 대해 지정 된 값은 크기 및 좌표가 아니라, 사각형이 비어 있는 경우를 제외 하 고 음수일 수 없습니다.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Z%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Y%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.X%2A>

trans-unit.source: An empty rectangle is specified by <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Empty%2A>, which has <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.X%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Y%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Z%2A> values of -Infinity.
trans-unit.target: 빈 사각형으로 지정 됩니다 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Empty%2A>, 변수가 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.X%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Y%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Z%2A>의-무한대 값.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Z%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Y%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.X%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D.Empty%2A>
